value.title: StarCraft 2: OLD SCHOOL vs NEW SCHOOL! (ShoWTimE vs MaxPax)
value.excerpt: Best-of-3 series between ShoWTimE and MaxPax in StarCraft 2. This is an old school progamer playing a very macro focused style, going up against a relative newcomer who plays far more aggressively. In this Protoss versus Protoss we see two of the highest ranked non-Korean players face off in a series.
